caption: So I've just been told(by the guy I have feelings for) that the only person I date has to scared of him, so if the guy upsets or hurts me, he has to answer to him, so then he won't make a move or try anything. But that's not what I want, and I don't think he understands, that I don't want someone who's scared of him, I want him. But he'll never fully understand how much he means to me, because he doesn't think he's worth it. He's insecure, and his insecurities break my heart. #help
song_album: I'll Be / Grind Me In the Gears [Digital 45] - Single
